  "final": "module RefModule(\n   input wire [3:0] a,\n   input wire [3:0] b,\n   output wire [3:0] result\n);  wire _n01 = a[0] ^ (2 * b)[0];\n  wire _c01 = a[0] & (2 * b)[0];\n  wire _n02 = a[1] ^ (2 * b)[1] ^ _c01;\n  wire _c02 = (a[1] & (2 * b)[1]) | (a[1] & _c01) | ((2 * b)[1] & _c01);\n  wire _n03 = a[2] ^ (2 * b)[2] ^ _c02;\n  wire _c03 = (a[2] & (2 * b)[2]) | (a[2] & _c02) | ((2 * b)[2] & _c02);\n  wire _n04 = a[3] ^ (2 * b)[3] ^ _c03;\n  wire _c04 = (a[3] & (2 * b)[3]) | (a[3] & _c03) | ((2 * b)[3] & _c03);\n  assign result = {_n01, _n02, _n03, _n04};\n\nendmodule"
